head_commit.message:
Fix some CI errors (#6)

* remove unused `concat_idents` crate attribute

* remove `doc` ci

GPPT (GIC-Partial-Passthrough) Virtual GICv3 implementation (#5)

* feat(vgic): implement GICD register handling and interrupt injection

- Add support for reading and writing GICD registers
- Implement interrupt injection for SGI, PPI, and SPI
- Refactor VGIC structure to include core-specific state
- Update handle_read and handle_write functions to support new registers
- Remove unused Vgicc struct

* refactor(vgic): restructure interrupt handling and improve code organization

- Restructure Interrupt and VgicInt types for better code organization
- Implement new functions for interrupt management
- Update Cargo.toml and Cargo.lock for new dependencies
- Modify constants and register definitions

* refactor(registers): improve register enum generation and naming consistency

- Update macro to generate GIC register enums with improved naming conventions
- Add comments for better code understanding
- Introduce new register variants for interrupt active set/clear, priority, target, configuration, and status
- Enhance readability and maintainability of register definitions

* feat(interrupt): implement basic interrupt handling functionality

- AddInterruptType and TriggerMode enums
- Update VgicInt struct to use new enums
- Implement enable/disable functionality for interrupts
- Add priority, vcpu_id, status

* refactor(vgic): remove unused VCpuIf parameter

- Remove VCpuIf parameter from handle_read and handle_write functions
- Update related function signatures in vgic.rs and devops_impl.rs
- Adjust implementation to remove unused vcpu argument
- Update vgicd.rs to initialize typer and iidr values

* refactor(vgic): update API and implement new functionality

- Update BaseDeviceOps trait implementation for Vgic
- Add support for byte, word, and dword access widths
- Implement interrupt injection using axvisor_api
- Refactor interrupt handling in VgicInt
- Update Vgic and Vgicd structs for new functionality

* remove `axhal` as dependency

* update arm_gicv2

* add vgicdv3

* wip: vgits

* finish vgits

* all codes included, to be refactored

* refactoring

* fix all previous CEs, update axvisor_api

* introduce `vgicv3` feature

* reorganize project

* add `new` for gicd, gicr, and gits v3

* add support of `GICD_IGRPMODR`, `GICR_IGRPMODR`, `GICR_IGROUPR` (passthrough)

* fix gits size

* fix gicd access mask calculation

* fix `DEFAULT_GITS_SIZE`

* add logs

* set `GICR_TYPER_LAST` for every GICR

* add more logs for lpi prop table

* add `VGicD::assign_irq` to explicitly assign an IRQ to a VCpu in a VM

* fix a mistake about `irq` calculation when accessing `GICD_ITARGETSR_RANGE`

* add dt and ct initialization, init cmdq, lpt, dt and ct before booting vms

* use main branch (merged) axdevice_base and axvisor_api

* remove .vscode folder

* remove `arm_gicv2` dep

* add github CI config

* formatted

* formatted all files

* update `memory_addr`

* fix some clippy errors
